snippet.textDisplay: Why Mata doesn't play more often I'll never know. Problem with Man U is they play when it's easy and when it's hard they decide that they don't feel like it. Serious lazy stream to this team. Sad to see what it's become. I blame Ed Woodward. He's totally brought down this club over decades of disgusting leadership. Cheapskate, no vision, control freak, loser. Well done to Solskjaer. He is doing a great job with very limited resources, lazy players and a squad full of entitlement. Nice to see Pogba off the pitch. Talented, but makes everyone's lives more difficult and forces everybody else to carry him so he can boast when the real heroes are the English lads behind the scenes making up for him and the other women's lack of integrity and work ethic. Keep up the good work Solskjaer!
